extends layout

block content
  .help-page
    h2.help-title Help & Support 🆘
    p.help-intro If you face any issues, please read the points below or contact our support team.

    h3.section-title 💡 General Help
    ul.help-list
      li New users must register with a username and password.
      li Admins have special privileges for adding shops and products.
      li If you forget your password, contact the admin to reset your account.
      li To add a product (Admin only): Go to Add Product → Fill details → Upload image → Submit.
      li To verify a product: Go to Scanner → Scan or enter barcode → View product details.
      li To find nearby shops: Open Nearby Shops → Click "View on Map" for directions.
      li To add a shop (Admin only): Enter Shop Name, Map Link, and Distance.
      li To write a review: Go to Reviews → Add your feedback about a product or shop.

    h3.section-title 🧑‍💻 Technical Support
    ul.help-list
      li If the app doesn’t load properly, refresh your browser or clear cache.
      li Make sure your internet connection is stable.
      li If images fail to upload, check file size and format.
      li Contact your admin for login or permission issues.

    h3.section-title 📞 Contact Support
    .contact-box
      p reach contact page
      p 🕒 <b>Support Hours:</b> 9 AM – 6 PM (Mon – Sat)
